        <p>For those people who want liberation from the habits created by his past in this life or from past life which are imprisoning him then, they can be assured that there is liberation. They have to follow the injunctions of Lord Krishna with full faith. This word faith is very important. The word used is Shraddha. Sri Aurobindo describes Śraddhā as “the soul’s belief in the Divine’s existence, wisdom, power, love and grace.”</p>

