        <p>Being neutral, being equanimous is the key and this equanimity should arise at the level of attraction/aversion and not control the gunas. This choosing is done at the level of intellect and an individual has to do this constantly to attain freedom. As per his Prakriti, the person may have attraction or repulsion towards certain things, so instead of controlling the basic qualities of a person, a person should exert his energies on the choice.</p>

