        <p>Those who worship the God with all love and affection for the God and not for objects created by him, in return God will bestow the spiritual intelligence where the individual consciousness unites with the supreme consciousness. God did not say that he will grant boons, money, heaven etc. He is simply saying that the individual consciousness will be united with the ultimate consciousness. The stakes are there for the person to choose, liberation from worldly pleasures/samsara or getting trapped into the worldly pleasures.</p>

